				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-7-C%E1%BB%91-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-t%C3%A1c-lang-bi%E1%BA%BFm-Thai-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%99-Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4ng-Ki%E1%BB%81n/poem-7W9_oz5KbHyRecrZub-UXQ">Bát ai thi kỳ 7 - Cố trước tác lang biếm Thai Châu tư hộ Huỳnh Dương Trịnh công Kiền - 八哀詩其七－故著作郎貶台州司戶滎陽鄭公虔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u-n%E1%BB%99i/poem-SsGvKrs_Ij4pVgXHaWo7Jw">Điệu nội - 悼內</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/M%E1%BB%99ng-Giang-Nam-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-_ZBf2ehrKK2aTgjWeTlsMg">Mộng Giang Nam kỳ 2 - 夢江南其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/author-VkIfi7DKP2f1cM8JZZP8yA">Ôn Đình Quân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-T7ykhmCIqNvTZ_L2JmhFFw">Nguyệt dạ - 月夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%C6%A1n-trung-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-b62WYTphBByLGp2yBthgXQ">Sơn trung tức sự - 山中即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ti%E1%BB%83u-nhi/poem-UXqkSYsIu9YnZO2PWGqZeQ">Tặng Vương thị tiểu nhi - 贈王氏小兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/author-qI9UHMMflLE3z07EmEsamw">Đậu Củng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href